            "description": "Converts cart to order in a single ACID transaction. Deducts inventory atomically. Clears cart on success.\n\n- **409** if a product went out of stock mid-transaction\n- **409** if this `Idempotency-Key` was already used (returns the existing order)\n- **400** if the cart is empty"
